*Hoffmeyer, Jesper. &quot;Signs of Meaning in the Universe&quot;. Bloomington: Indiana University Press. (1996)
*Kull, Kalevi. Choosing and learning: Semiosis means choice. &quot;Sign Systems Studies&quot; 46(4): 452–466. (2018)</text><links>
